			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	ShopRepublic is a newly established Internet Startup led by 2 partners with a lot of enthusiasm and extensive experience in the creation and funding of Internet companies. We have the strategic support of experts in technical, commercial, online marketing and internationalization, and are backed by private investors and professionals in the sector.</p>
<p>
	ShopRepublic aggregates promotional discounts from online stores and service providers worldwide. On one hand, helps users save money by finding the best deals for a product, brand or shop online and on the other, allows them to discover new international stores that deliver what they are looking for in their area.</p>
<p>
	ShopRepublic users share their deals and shopping knowledge through other channels. As a reward for all these actions, receive real and virtual incentives, thereby experiencing a similar dynamic to social games. ShopRepublic is about to launch, having been developed in India.</p>
<p>
	Main tasks:</p>
<p>
	- Internalize current platform&rsquo;s code and architecture in order to take it forward and improve.  </p>
<p>
	- Participate in the definition of new features for the platform, both for the front and back end.</p>
<p>
	 - Prepare system requirements, models, components and interface for these features  </p>
<p>
	- To engage actively in the development of the platform, sharing duties with the team in India  </p>
<p>
	- Build a framework for smooth and efficient communication with the rest of the development team</p>
<p>
	 - Conduct R &amp; D on technologies and implement them together with the rest of the development team.</p>
